posting_body: ["Embrace classic comfort and contemporary style at 3300 Tamarac Apartments, in Denver's Hampden neighborhood.", 'Our collection of refined studio, 1 & 2 bedroom apartments offer you a place to rest, relax, and have a little fun.', 'From our relaxed modern style and upscale social spaces to chic interiors, youll be ready to unwind in no time.', '-Landscaped courtyards and ponds with outdoor seating', '-Wood-style plank flooring in kitchen and living areas', '-Resident social lounge with demonstration kitchen and billiards table', '-Reserved covered parking                                                                                    Photo                                                                                                                                 Featured amenity', '-Virtual Moving Concierge: Complimentary address change, set up home services and digital moving announcements', '-Onsite playground', '-Move-in with NO SECURITY DEPOSIT:', 'Only a small one-time payment', '-3 relaxing pools with expansive sundecks', '-Renovated unit', '-Fenced dog park with pet watering station', '-9-foot ceilings', '-Private balcony or patio                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Featured amenity', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
